One of the best moments in my career as a DP was conducting interviews with great professors and young doctors/investigators. This experience took me back to my high school days when I wanted to be an engineer but found myself in the medical field before quitting to pursue dance and film arts. It also made me realize I am on the right path to be in the same room, listening to professors I once read about in books, and shaking hands not as a scientist, but as a filmmaker.

This experience will always be memorable for me.

Shout out to the new Friends I made🤣
